text: Adikhalamani was a Nubian king of Kush, ruling from Meroë in the first half of the 2nd century BCE. ==Titles== *Prenomen: Titenre Setepnetjeru ("Image of Re, chosen of the Gods") *Nomen: Adikhalamani with epithet MeryisetTörök, László.
